`,Hq=`/*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*\\
  Choupo electrolyte catalogue --- PITZER cation-anion parameters (25 C base).

  Source: USGS PHREEQC pitzer.dat (public domain); values from Appelo et al.
  (Geochim. Cosmochim. Acta 125 (2014) 49; Appl. Geochem. 55 (2015) 62).
  alpha1 = 1.4 for 2:2 salts (beta2 active), else 2.0; alpha2 = 12.
  25 C base only (the file T,P coefficients are deferred). Per-row gamma_pm
  validation (AAD vs literature) is recorded by the curation swarm.
\\*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

